---
title: Double Sweet Soy Chicken & Asian Chilli Slaw with Sesame Kūmara Fries & Mayo
description: This chicken has layers upon layers of flavour, first being cooked in our staple sweet-soy seasoning, then being tossed in sweet chilli! Sesame-crusted kūmara fries and a crunchy, zingy slaw act as the perfect side-kicks to this superstar dish.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663c73c092f430b61ffd6515-8adb6368-245c8bd7.jpeg
